! Toolbar Styles

10 different styles for the editor toolbar buttons, from elegant to fancy to crazy.

!! Available Styles

|!Style |!Description |
|`minimal` |Clean, invisible buttons with subtle hover effects |
|`flat` |Modern flat design with subtle backgrounds (default) |
|`outlined` |Elegant outlined buttons with border effects |
|`rounded` |Soft, pill-shaped buttons with shadows |
|`elevated` |Material design inspired with depth and shadows |
|`gradient` |Colorful gradient backgrounds |
|`glass` |Frosted glass effect (glassmorphism) |
|`neon` |Glowing neon cyberpunk effect |
|`retro` |Vintage 3D button style (Windows 95 vibes) |
|`brutalist` |Bold, stark, attention-grabbing design |

!! Configuration

Set your preferred style in `$:/config/codemirror-6/toolbars/style`

Or use the Control Panel: ''Settings → CodeMirror → Toolbar Style''
